but is it a phone?</a>
<a href="flaky-products/IndiaTelco.html">Speak not lightly of 
2G, 3G, 32768G</a>.</dd>

<dt>Indian IT "innovation", defined.</dt>
<dd><a href="flaky-products/TvseBharat.html">Euphoria
through reduced expectations</a>.</dd>

